  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nValidation time of `voluntary_exit` message is sometimes very high although its logic is simple\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1263\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-22 at 13 29 16\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/233766926-e7cca3ec-d53a-4f74-858b-6cc5312798b3.png\">\r\n\r\nprobably it's due to the Job Wait time when we try to get head state at current epoch\r\n<img width=\"1305\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-22 at 13 30 44\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/233766994-64245d37-6669-4faa-b92b-9bf098dcd23f.png\">\r\n\r\nthe bigger concern is we may use the regen queue unnecessarily here, a lot of time head state should be in the same epoch so we don't need the regen queue. Note that `getBlockSlotState() api` for gossip block validation should be as fast as possible so other consumers should not use this api unless it's really necessary\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nLow validation time consistently\r\n\r\n",
